data.title: JJ Redick Orlando Magic 8 x 10 Signed 0784/3000 Team Give Away
data.meta_description: This 8 x 10 photo features NBA player J J Redick in his Orlando Magic team uniform. The photo has been signed by Redick and is one of only 3000 produced as a team giveaway. The authenticity of the signature has been verified by Orlando Magic. This is a must-have for any basketball fan and would make a great addition to any fan collection. The photo is in excellent condition and ready for display.
